text.text: Facilities are well kept including the badmin hall. However I cannot find any shower facilities   after my badminton game even after roaming around the area for 15 mins. I only know from the previous visits that there are shower facilities inside the swimming pool area but the pool is paid entry.

text.text:
Good stadium with a plethora of activities available like a gym, table tennis, football, and more. There is a pizza hut/KFC built in the stadium. Not the best choice of restaurant to put in a place built for improving health, but convenient nonetheless.

1 star off because the football pitch quality is not the best. Sliding with socks will still burn you and without socks you are gonna get an open wound.
